  "remarks": "\nVitalyi Stasiukevich is the Deputy Chief of Public Security Police in Grodno. In this position he bears responsibility for the inhumane and degrading treatment, amounting to serious human rights violations, including torture, carried out in the detention facilities following the elections of 9 August.",
